
The pmonitor v2 is extended to support p and m transformation. 

Usage:

For p transformation:

1. load pminitorV2-20210703.maude 

1.5 load sampling-lib.maude

2. load input-modules/pi-query.maude 

3. (p-trans QUERY .)
Advisory: Module QUERY redefined.
New module P-QUERY generated!

4. load input-modules/init-query.maude 

5. (p-init INIT-QUERY .)
New module P-INIT-QUERY generated!

6. (show module P-INIT-QUERY .)


For m transformation with p 

1. load input-modules/events-query.maude 

2. (pm-trans QUERY .)
Advisory: Module QUERY redefined.
New module M-P-QUERY generated!

3. load input-modules/init-query.maude 

4. (pm-init INIT-QUERY .)
New module M-P-INIT-QUERY generated!

5. (show module M-P-INIT-QUERY .)
